descriptionHtml:
Included is the converted heightmap to playable landmass. It is using ONRA's Tamriel BMP and some modification in GEOCONTROL 2. To play this you need to add a door to it in the Creation Kit. I created this after I was looking for a heightmap for Highrock but couldn't find one. As I am moving on with my project and making the region by hand, I really don't need this anymore. So I uploaded it as a resource for others.

Work still required: Fix the water distance between highrock and Hammerfell, GEOCONTROL messed up the distance.



Thank you Onra for your work with the oblivion series that gave me the resources I needed.
author: 14manj01
